author: Alex Lubben, Anne Torpey
title: Can You Get Coronavirus Twice? 116 South Koreans Have Tested Positive After Recovering
description: It may be that the virus is “reactivating,” and the patients are experiencing something more like a relapse than a second case.
content:
The South Korean government says that more than a hundred people have tested positive for the coronavirus a second time. And the World Health Organization is investigating to see whats really happening.
